summary:
I've been getting two or three phone calls a day from this number trying to sell me stuff on my mobile this past week.
I've...
body:
I’ve been getting two or three phone calls a day from this number trying to sell me stuff on my mobile this past week.

I’ve since blocked them, but not till after the last phone call when they phoned asking for me and I straight up just went “I’m sorry she can’t come to the phone right now” and surprisingly they said “why?” And I actually got to say “why?…oh…cause she’s dead.” And I hung up the phone and blocked their number.

I’m feeling like a winner.
